00:18.653 --> 00:21.598
What did you think?
I wasn't gonna find out, Russell?

00:21.598 --> 00:24.380
You are such a heartless bastard!

00:24.380 --> 00:27.769
Paula! Let go.

00:30.478 --> 00:33.286
If you show up with one
of your whores tonight, Russell,

00:33.286 --> 00:36.453
I swear to God you'll regret it!

00:37.744 --> 00:40.552
What's the matter, Jason?
You're not hungry?

00:40.552 --> 00:41.944
He's been throwing up.

00:41.944 --> 00:44.731
I think he's nervous about
singing at the recital tonight.

00:44.731 --> 00:47.159
God gave you a beautiful gift.

00:47.159 --> 00:48.661
And he'll give you the courage to use it.

00:48.661 --> 00:50.708
Stupid son of a bitch.!

00:50.708 --> 00:53.303
All I did is try and find out when
he was coming to the recital tonight,

00:53.303 --> 00:56.246
and he practically ran me over.

00:57.185 --> 01:01.183
You children, go get ready for school.

01:02.740 --> 01:04.419
If your father tries to talk to you tonight,

01:04.419 --> 01:07.396
make sure you get me or Helen, okay?

01:09.502 --> 01:12.547
We'll be there at 6:45, okay?

01:12.547 --> 01:14.310
Okay, we'll see you then.

01:14.310 --> 01:15.805
Oh, my poor brother.

01:15.805 --> 01:19.173
Paula had some kind of screaming fit
in front of his office this morning.

01:19.173 --> 01:21.244
About tonight, Brenda,
I'm gonna be late.

01:21.244 --> 01:23.248
I have to wait for some test results.

01:23.248 --> 01:27.024
- Okay. I'll see you soon.
- Okay, bye.

01:28.682 --> 01:30.771
How's Jason?
Is he feeling better?

01:30.771 --> 01:33.033
He's still in the bathroom throwing up.

01:33.033 --> 01:34.468
Maybe I should go back.

01:34.468 --> 01:37.631
Sam says he will be fine.
I'm sure he will.

01:37.631 --> 01:39.654
Has my future ex arrived?

01:39.654 --> 01:42.476
No.
But his sister's here.

01:45.031 --> 01:47.463
Hey. Did you see Russell out there?

01:47.463 --> 01:50.077
No. He hasn't shown up?

01:50.077 --> 01:51.632
I should call him.

01:51.632 --> 01:54.326
Sam said Jason's been sick all day.

01:58.085 --> 02:01.446
Here comes trouble.

02:01.446 --> 02:04.062
You're late.

